{"tid":872612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【我喺一隻狗】張建宗感興奮：中國人驕傲光榮　料習近平發言談大灣區","createTime":"2018-10-23T00:25:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T13:30:43.000Z","uid":195944,"like":43,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e4f3ff7f1e550699f094472a14b2107ad7d82efb","tid":872612,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T00:25:31.000Z","msg":"港珠澳大橋開通儀式今早9時於珠海舉行，預料國家主席習近平將主持儀式。有份出席的政務司長張建宗早上表示，不知道習近平發言內容，但相信會談及粵港澳大灣區及國家發展。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗形容自己心情興奮，強調大橋是世紀工程、是中國人的驕傲和光榮。他指出，三地首次合作是創舉，期望香港進一步促進與內地交通、貿易、人流物流資金流，以及帶動香港經濟發展。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗另提到，大橋香港口岸區坐落大嶼山，而大嶼山能進入內地，亦能進入機場，發揮對內對外交通「雙門戶」作用，具有重要策略意義。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181023/s00001/1540252682316\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181023%2Fs00001%2F1540252682316&d=HDdcVWKqnhaKed%2FWU9HMkPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=a15e2a71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181023%2Fs00001%2F1540252682316&h=e503cbd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181023/s00001/1540252682316</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果我係記者就會問光頭佬 你攞咗大陸身份證未？<br />\n<br />\n如果未, 係咪即係唔支持蟈家？係咪叛蟈？<br />\n答忙就會問, 忙重要過承認狆蟈人身份？係咪想搞分離？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a5f422ac4066bfce99f34fbbc73088b1b60511","tid":872612,"uid":65061,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T00:30:20.000Z","msg":"奴才既奴才<br />\n不知所謂"},{"pid":"c733f7fb128ff699e39ca402cddc563dc957ef1d","tid":872612,"uid":43041,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T00:31:03.000Z","msg":"連登仔前排又話d官唔會再提大灣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b255133fac22321a58e39898ba12a7278ed80839","tid":872612,"uid":195944,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T00:36:18.000Z","msg":"起都未起好就要通車？<br />\n<br />\n點解要咁急呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咪隻維尼狗急住落黎香港攞錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae3beb70adb0ff5b13140a26605a312934523c3","tid":872612,"uid":49215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T00:38:27.000Z","msg":"一國一制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"818992808cb75596a361f419fb6c08996e7ebd63","tid":872612,"uid":195944,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T00:47:30.000Z","msg":"胡應傷有無得去大橋吠兩下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca363d438abb7d5986c54b4a9359068f973aef61","tid":872612,"uid":42044,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T01:02:51.000Z","msg":"剩係中國人先會做一樣嘢就驕傲到出晒臉，其他國家做到所有嘢都完善都冇咁嘅心態，我身為黃種人都感到好撚核凸。"},{"pid":"5d7fe02ca1d6270f154fe490da536a5f51b8503c","tid":872612,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T01:06:10.000Z","msg":"屎坑都有去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關佢咩事？"},{"pid":"57f00343ff0dee1ad860f0d0c4b91114acac8145","tid":872612,"uid":195944,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T01:10:12.000Z","msg":"愛蟈振英都有去<br />\n<br /